Perfect day

This skill keep you motivated by giving motivational thoughts, helps you stretch and manages your to do list in alexa App

this skill is an attempt to make Alexa more personalized. Like giving the responses based on weather it was its first invocation or second.And also based on at what time of the day the skill is invoked.Also calling the user by his/her name. 
Currently this skill helps users in three ways
1st) In Motivating user by telling motivational thoughts
2nd) In stretching by giving simple and quick Stretch follow through option
3rd) By managing users TO-DO list (In Alexa App) by reading and writing in TO-DO  list


Alexa open perfect day

Alexa ask perfect day for motivation

Alexa ask perfect day for stretch

motivation, stretch, health, help, to, do, list, list, management, assistant

